videoDetails.Title: Stereo Madness in Desmos Graphing Calculator — Geometry Dash
videoDetails.Description:
Recreation of level Stereo Madness in Desmos Graphing Calculator.
The graph: https://bit.ly/3ApvwzR
To start the level, you need to click on the play button next to the expression "f = 1". It doesn't work in mobile app, you need to open it in browser.

Also I can record any your level in high quality. Write to me in Discord (LeTim#2685).
